'''''Carpagian''''' was a [[Saryabo IV Pinnace Scoutcraft]] owned by the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]]. It was given to the group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] who attempted to meet with a defecting [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]], [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Joser]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dandrian]]. When it got there, the Rebels were was ordered to land in [[Docking Bay 107]] in [[Lon Drasna]], which is where the ship stayed while the Rebels learned that Joser was held captive in [[Alpha-Omega Prison]] on the orbiting [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] [[Alpha-Omega]]. The Rebels landed the ship on the asteroid close to the prison and proceeded to rescue Joser from Imperial control before [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] arrived.

